info.name: Veg Masala Maggi
info.description: Introducing Vegetable Maggi, a delicious variation of the classic Maggi noodles that is packed with the goodness of vegetables. Vegetable Maggi offers the same convenience and comforting taste as traditional Maggi noodles, but with an added nutritious twist

info.name: Poha Home Stlye [180 Gms]
info.description: Experience the simplicity and delightful flavors of our Poha, a traditional Indian dish that is sure to awaken your taste buds. Immerse yourself in the fragrant aromas, the soft yet textured rice flakes, and the harmonious blend of spices and vegetables. Whether enjoyed as a breakfast or snack, our Poha is a satisfying and comforting choice that will leave you wanting more

info.name: Masala Maggi
info.description: Whether you enjoy Maggi noodles as a quick snack, a late-night meal, or a go-to option during busy days, they offer a reliable and satisfying choice. The nostalgic and comforting taste of Maggi noodles has made them a popular favorite among people of all ages

info.name: Thepla [2 Piece]
info.description: Our Thepla is not only delicious but also a healthy option. The whole wheat flour provides dietary fiber and nutrients, while the addition of fenugreek leaves offers numerous health benefits, including aiding digestion and regulating blood sugar

info.name: Handvo [220 Gms]
info.description: Introducing Handva, a savory and wholesome Gujarati snack that is both flavorful and nutritious. Handva, also known as Handvo, is a traditional Indian dish made from a fermented batter of rice, lentils, and vegetables.

info.name: Upma [200 Gms]
info.description: Our Upma is not only delicious but also a nutritious choice. Semolina is a good source of carbohydrates and provides energy, while the vegetables add essential vitamins, minerals, and dietary fiber.

info.name: Veg. Poha Home Stlye [180 Gms]
info.description: Experience the simplicity and delightful flavors of our Poha with assorted vegetables, a traditional Indian dish that is sure to awaken your taste buds. Immerse yourself in the fragrant aromas, the soft yet textured rice flakes, and the harmonious blend of spices and vegetables. Whether enjoyed as a breakfast or snack, our Poha is a satisfying and comforting choice that will leave you wanting more

info.name: Cheese Corn Maggi
info.description: Cheese corn Maggi, a delicious variation of the classic Maggi noodles that is packed with the goodness of corn. Maggi offers the same convenience and comforting taste as traditional Maggi noodles, but with an added nutritious twist

info.name: Oats [180gms]
info.description: Masala oats offer a convenient and nutritious option for those looking to incorporate more whole grains and flavorful spices into their diet. They can be enjoyed for breakfast, lunch, or dinner, providing a satisfying flavourful meal that is both nourishing and delicious.

info.name: Veg. Upma [200gms]
info.description: With assorted vegebles our Upma is not only delicious but also a nutritious choice. Semolina is a good source of carbohydrates and provides energy, while the vegetables add essential vitamins, minerals, and dietary fiber.

info.name: Aloo Paratha [2 Piece]
info.description: Savor the authentic flavors of India with our Aloo Paratha! This classic dish features a tender, flaky flatbread stuffed with a delicious filling of spiced mashed potatoes, fresh herbs, and aromatic spices

info.name: Adrak Wali Chai
info.description: Made to order with natural ingredients with fresh ginger and selected tea leaves, this delicious blend is a tasty way to sip at work or at home

info.name: Adrak Masala Chai
info.description: Indulge in the ritual of savoring a cup of Masala Chai, whether as a morning pick-me-up, an afternoon delight, or a cozy companion on chilly evenings. Let the flavors of the spices transport you to a land of ancient traditions and soul-nourishing warmth

info.name: Adrak Elaichi Chai
info.description: The addition of ginger to elaichi chai provides an extra warming and soothing element that is perfect for cooler weather or anytime you need a comforting beverage.The fragrance and taste of elaichi provide a delicious compliment to the spiciness of ginger

info.name: Adrak Mint Chai
info.description: Minty Warm, the Ginger Pudina is the definition of cozy, this season! It is a blend of aromatic tea leaves, warmth of ginger and freshness of cool mint leaves added to sugar and milk made with extra love just for you.

info.name: Elaichi Wali Chai
info.description: Elaichi tea offers a unique flavor profile that is both refreshing and soothing. The natural sweetness and warmth of cardamom add depth to the tea, enhancing its overall taste.

info.name: Adrak Lemongrass
info.description: Introducing our Ginger Lemongrass Chai, a tantalizing blend that combines the warming spice of ginger, the zesty freshness of lemongrass, and the rich flavours of traditional chai tea. Immerse yourself in the invigorating aromas, vibrant flavours, and soothing qualities of this unique fusion.

info.name: Kesari Elaichi Chai
info.description: Introducing our Saffron Cardamom Tea, a luxurious blend that combines the delicate floral notes of saffron with the warm, aromatic spice of cardamom. Immerse yourself in the opulence of this exquisite infusion that delivers a sensory experience like no other.

info.name: Mint Masala Chai
info.description: Mint masala chai, is a delightful and refreshing variation of traditional Indian masala chai. This flavorful and aromatic beverage combines the soothing qualities of black tea with the invigorating essence of fresh mint leaves and a blend of spices.

info.name: Muska Bun
info.description: A Maska Bun, you can expect a delightful burst of flavors, combining the simple yet comforting taste of butter with the softness of the bun, making it an irresistible treat for your taste buds.

info.name: Cheese Garlic Bread
info.description: A tantalizing combination of savory garlic, rich butter, and oozy melted cheese. The aroma of the baked garlic and cheese is incredibly inviting, making it difficult to resist (4 Pieces)

info.name: Butter Bread Toast
info.description: Once the bread is toasted, a generous amount of butter spread onto each slice while they are still warm. The butter will melt into the bread, creating a rich and creamy layer that adds a delightful flavour and texture to the toast.

info.name: Bread Butter
info.description: Experience the simplicity and satisfaction of Bread and Butter, a timeless combination that brings together the comforting flavours of soft bread and creamy butter. Bread and Butter offers a delightful and comforting treat that never goes out of style.

info.name: Jam Muska Bun
info.description: Introducing our delightful Jam Maska Bun, a tantalizing combination of a soft, buttery bun and a luscious layer of sweet and fruity jam. It's a perfect treat for those who crave a balance of flavors that will satisfy their sweet tooth.

info.name: Chocolate Muska Bun
info.description: Experience the sheer pleasure of our Chocolate Maska Bun. With its divine chocolate filling, buttery Maska layer, and heavenly soft bun. Treat yourself to this delightful creation and savor the harmonious blend of chocolate and Maska in every bite.

info.name: Signature Nutella Muska Bun
info.description: Indulge your sweet tooth with our delectable Nutella Muska Bun! Originating from the streets of Mumbai, this heavenly treat features a soft and fluffy bun, generously filled with rich and creamy Nutella spread.

info.name: Jam Bread Butter
info.description: Jam bread butter is a delightful and classic combination of flavors that brings together the sweetness of jam, the creaminess of butter, and the softness of bread.

info.name: Strawberry Muska Bun
info.description: Treat yourself to a delightful burst of sweetness with our Strawberry Muska Bun! Inspired by the flavors of summer, this indulgent treat features a soft and pillowy bun filled with luscious strawberry compote.

info.name: Adrak Mint Chai (serves For 4 )
info.description: Our tea is made fresh on every order, to ensure the highest quality. We hope you enjoy the fresh taste of our ginger mint chai! Let us bring our fresh and different flavor combinations to your home or office, we can deliver chai on demand

info.name: Adrak Elaichi Chai (serves For 4 )
info.description: The warmth and spiciness of ginger, combined with the aromatic essence of cardamom, create a deliciously balanced flavor profile. The gentle heat from the ginger adds a comforting element, while the cardamom contributes a subtle sweetness and a hint of herbal freshness.

info.name: Adrak Wali Chai (serves For 4 )
info.description: Made to order with natural ingredients with fresh ginger and selected tea leaves, this delicious blend is a tasty way to sip at work or at home..

info.name: Elaichi Wali Chai (serves For 4 )
info.description: Elaichi tea is a wonderful choice that combines the goodness of tea with the unique essence of cardamom. It's a beverage that not only pleases the taste buds but also offers a comforting and aromatic experience with each sip.

info.name: Kesari Elaichi Chai (serves For 4 )
info.description: Complementing the saffron, we incorporate the captivating spice of cardamom. Cardamom pods are carefully crushed to release their warm, citrusy aroma and reveal tiny seeds that infuse the tea with their rich, aromatic flavors. The combination of saffron and cardamom creates a symphony of taste that is both invigorating and indulgent.

info.name: Adrak Masala Chai (serves For 4 )
info.description: Introducing our Masala Chai, a captivating and aromatic blend of traditional Indian spices and robust  tea with the warmth of fresh ginger. Immerse yourself in the rich flavors, enticing aromas, and the comforting warmth of this beloved spiced tea.

info.name: Adrak Lemongrass Chai (serves For 4 )
info.description: Indulge in the captivating flavours and soothing qualities of our Ginger Lemongrass Chai. Experience the perfect harmony of ginger, lemongrass, and traditional chai tea. Elevate your tea-drinking experience and embark on a journey of invigorating flavors that will awaken your senses and bring a sense of balance and rejuvenation to your day.

info.name: Mint Masala Chai (served For 4)
info.description: Mint masala chai, is a delightful and refreshing variation of traditional Indian masala chai. This flavorful and aromatic beverage combines the soothing qualities of black tea with the invigorating essence of fresh mint leaves and a blend of spices.

info.name: Cheese Corn Grilled Sandwich (3 Layer)
info.description: Experience a mouthwatering combination of flavors and textures with our Cheese Corn Grilled Sandwich. This delightful sandwich brings together the creamy richness of cheese and the sweet crunch of corn, all perfectly grilled to create a crispy and satisfying meal.

info.name: Mumbai Style Veg. Grilled Sandwich (3 Layer)
info.description: Experience the vibrant flavors of Mumbai street food with our Mumbai Style Veg Grilled Sandwich! A beloved classic, this sandwich is a symphony of textures and tastes, packed with an assortment of savory and spicy fillings.

info.name: Paneer Tikka Grilled Sandwich (3 Layer)
info.description: Indulge in the tantalizing flavors of India with our Paneer Tikka Grilled Sandwich! This mouthwatering creation features succulent cubes of paneer marinated in a medley of aromatic spices and grilled to perfection

info.name: Spicy Mexican Grilled Sandwich (3 Layer)
info.description: Indulge in the fiery and savory flavors of our Spicy Mexican Grilled Sandwich and let it transport you to the vibrant streets of Mexico. Enjoy the bold, zesty, and satisfying flavors of this culinary adventure, and savor the deliciousness that awaits in every mouthwatering bite.

info.name: Junglee Grilled Sandwich (3 Layer)
info.description: Embark on a refreshing culinary adventure with our Carrot, Cabbage, and Mint Flavour Junglee Sandwich! This innovative twist on the classic Junglee Sandwich combines the earthy sweetness of carrots, the crispness of cabbage, and the invigorating freshness of mint leaves

info.name: Schewan Paneer Grilled Sandwich
info.description: Elevate your taste buds with our fiery Schezwan Paneer Grilled Sandwich! This fusion masterpiece brings together the bold flavors of Schezwan cuisine with the comfort of a grilled sandwich.

info.name: Aloo Mutter Grilled Sandwich (3 Layer)
info.description: This scrumptious sandwich brings together the earthy goodness of potatoes, the sweetness of green peas, and a medley of aromatic spices, all grilled to perfection for a satisfying and wholesome meal.

info.name: Veg. Spicy Coleslaw Grilled Sandwich (3 Layer)
info.description: This delightful sandwich combines the aromatic spices of a traditional Kadhai Paneer dish with the indulgence of a grilled sandwich, creating a fusion of tastes that will transport you to the streets of India.

info.name: Punjabi Samosa [2 Piece]
info.description: Experience the authentic flavors of Punjab with a healthier twist with our Air-Fried Punjabi Samosa. This delightful snack captures the essence of traditional Punjabi samosas while offering a lighter and guilt-free option.

info.name: French Fries
info.description: Indulge in the classic and timeless delight of French Fries. Our carefully crafted fries are the perfect balance of crispy golden exterior and soft, fluffy interior, making them a delicious treat that is loved by people of all ages.

info.name: Peri Peri Fries
info.description: These delectable fries are seasoned with a vibrant blend of spices inspired by the popular Peri Peri seasoning, adding a delightful kick to your snacking experience.

info.name: Lemon Garlic French Fries
info.description: Each fries is perfectly seasoned with a savory blend of garlic powder, lemon zest, and a touch of salt, offering a burst of tanginess and richness that will leave your taste buds craving for more.

info.name: Smokey French Fries
info.description: Indulge in a mouthwatering flavor explosion with our Smokey BBQ French Fries! Crispy golden fries are tossed in our signature blend of smoky barbecue seasoning, delivering a tantalizing combination of savory, sweet, and spicy flavors

info.name: Classic Cold Coffee
info.description: Our Cold Coffee is conveniently packaged and ready to enjoy on the go. Whether you're looking for a quick pick-me-up in the morning, a refreshing afternoon treat, or a delightful beverage for any time of day, our Cold Coffee is the perfect choice.

info.name: Chocolate Cold Coffee
info.description: Chocolate cold coffee is a delicious and refreshing beverage that combines the flavors of coffee and chocolate in a chilled and creamy drink. It is a popular choice for coffee and chocolate lovers who enjoy a cold and indulgent treat

info.name: Cold Bournvita
info.description: Cold Bournvita is a delicious and refreshing beverage that brings together the chocolatey goodness of Bournvita with a chilled and creamy twist.

info.name: Hazelenut Cold Coffee
info.description: Indulge in the luxurious combination of coffee and hazelnut with our Hazelnut Cold Coffee. It's a refreshing, creamy, and nutty beverage that will satisfy your coffee cravings while providing a delightful twist. Treat yourself to this delectable experience and elevate your coffee enjoyment to new heights

info.name: Vanila Cold Coffee
info.description: Whether you prefer it hot or iced, vanilla coffee offers a wonderful balance of flavors that will satisfy both coffee enthusiasts and those with a sweet tooth. So, sit back, relax, and savor the enticing blend of coffee and vanilla in every sip.

info.name: Classic Coffee
info.description: Treat yourself to the unparalleled pleasure of our Coffee and savor each sip as it transports you to a realm of pure coffee bliss

info.name: Hot Chocolate
info.description: A warm and delightful beverage that offers a rich and velvety chocolate flavor with marshmello. Each sip is a heavenly experience, with the creamy texture of milk and the decadent sweetness of chocolate coming together in perfect harmony.

info.name: Hot Bournvita
info.description: a delightful and indulgent drink that offers a rich and velvety chocolate taste with a hint of malt. Hot Bournvita provides a comforting and satisfying experience, especially during colder months or when you're in need of a pick-me-up.

info.name: Hazelenut Coffee
info.description: A harmonious blend where the bold and robust flavors of coffee are complemented by the smooth and slightly sweet notes of hazelnut. The hazelnut adds a creamy and nutty quality to the coffee, enhancing its overall taste profile.

info.name: Vanila Coffee
info.description: Whether you prefer it hot or iced, vanilla coffee offers a wonderful balance of flavors that will satisfy both coffee enthusiasts and those with a sweet tooth. So, sit back, relax, and savor the enticing blend of coffee and vanilla in every sip.

info.name: Chocolate Coffee
info.description: The aroma of hot chocolate coffee is inviting, with the scent of freshly brewed coffee intertwining with the rich aroma of chocolate. Each sip offers a delightful balance of flavors, combining the robustness of coffee with the creamy, chocolaty sweetness of hot chocolate.

info.name: Apna Aam Panna
info.description: Aampanna Cooler is the ultimate thirst quencher for those scorching summer days.

info.name: Iced Lychee
info.description: Our Iced Lychee Cooler is a delightful symphony of sweet and tangy flavors, perfect for quenching your thirst on a hot summer's day or any time you crave a tropical escape.

info.name: Mangoo Sip
info.description: Indulge in the tropical paradise with our refreshing Mango Breeze Bliss. Crafted with the finest ripe mangoes, this vibrant concoction will transport your taste buds to sun-kissed beaches and swaying palm trees.

info.name: Strawberry Mint Cooler
info.description: Indulge in the refreshing embrace of our Strawberry Mint Cooler, a tantalizing fusion of ripe strawberries and freshly picked mint leaves.

info.name: Kesar Masala Milk
info.description: Kesar Masala Milk, Also Known As Saffron Spiced Milk, Is A Delightful And Aromatic Indian Beverage That Combines The Richness Of Milk With The Exotic Flavors Of Saffron, Various Spices.

info.name: Haldi Adrak Milk
info.description: (Serves 200Ml) Haldi Adrak Milk, Also Known As Turmeric Ginger Milk, Is A Popular And Soothing Beverage That Combines The Health Benefits Of Turmeric And Ginger With The Comfort Of Warm Milk.

info.name: Hot And Sweet Milk
info.description: (Serves 200Ml) Hot Milk With Sugar/Gud Is A Comforting And Delightful Beverage That Offers A Simple Yet Satisfying Experience. This Classic Drink Is Made By Heating Milk To A Gentle Simmer And Then Adding An Appropriate Amount Of Sugar Or Gud To Enhance Its Flavor And Sweetness.

info.name: Hot Ginger Milk (ukado)
info.description: (Serves 200Ml) Hot Ginger Milk Is A Soothing Beverage That Combines The Goodness Of Milk And The Health Benefits Of Ginger. This Warm And Comforting Drink Is Known For Its Potential Positive Effects On Health.

info.name: Peach Ice Tea
info.description: Indulge in the delightful taste of summer with our Peach Ice Tea. This refreshing beverage combines the natural sweetness of ripe peaches with the soothing qualities of tea, creating a harmonious blend of flavors that will transport you to a sun-kissed orchard with every sip.

info.name: Lemon Ice Tea
info.description: Quench your thirst and refresh your senses with our invigorating Lemon Ice Tea. This delightful beverage combines the zesty tang of fresh lemons with the cool and soothing qualities of tea, creating a perfect balance of flavors that will revitalize you with every sip.

info.name: Lemon Mint Ice Tea
info.description: Served over ice, our Lemon Mint Ice Tea provides a revitalizing and thirst-quenching experience, making it the ideal drink for hot summer days or whenever you need a refreshing pick-me-up.

info.name: Strawberry Ice Tea
info.description: Savor the taste of summer with our delightful Strawberry Iced Tea. Made with freshly brewed tea infused with succulent strawberries, this beverage is a burst of fruity sweetness with a hint of tartness.
